TASKNAME=Recursively list all files, including hidden ones.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if present the file ~/agent_test/test2.3.txt
TASKCOMMAND=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo list all files, including hidden ones in the home folder and put the content in the file ~/agent_test/test2.3.txt. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check if the file ~/agent_test/test2.3.txt is created and return the content of this file.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if present the file ~/agent_test/test2.3.txt
